  "faq": {
    "title": "FAQ / Help",
    "helpTitle": "How can we help you?",
    "helpDesc": "Find answers to the most frequently asked questions here.",
    "contactTitle": "Didn't find your answer?",
    "contactDesc": "Our support team is here to help you.",
    "contactBtn": "Contact us",
    "q1": "How to declare a lost document?",
    "r1": "Go to the \"Declare\" tab and select \"For me\". Choose the document type, fill in the required fields, then submit. You will receive a reference number to track your declaration.",
    "q2": "How to declare a found document?",
    "r2": "Go to \"I found a document\" in the \"Found\" tab. Take a photo of the document and fill in the form. The owner will be notified if the document is registered in our system.",
    "q3": "How does matching work?",
    "r3": "When a loss declaration and a found declaration match (same document type, same city), our system sends a notification to both parties to facilitate return.",
    "q4": "Can I track my declarations?",
    "r4": "Yes, go to the \"Declarations\" tab to see the history and status of all your declarations (loss or found).",
    "q5": "How to save a document in my vault?",
    "r5": "Go to the \"Documents\" tab and press the \"+\" button to scan or import a document. It will be securely saved in your personal space.",
    "q6": "How to add a device (phone, computer)?",
    "r6": "In the \"Devices\" tab, press \"Add a device\". Fill in the information (brand, model, serial number, etc.). In case of loss, you can quickly report the device as lost.",
    "q7": "How to edit my personal information?",
    "r7": "Go to the \"Profile\" tab, press the pencil icon on the top right to edit your profile (name, email, phone, password).",
    "q8": "How to refer friends?",
    "r8": "In the \"Profile\" tab, select \"Refer friends\". You will receive a referral code to share. When a friend signs up with your code, you earn bonus points.",
    "q9": "How to contact support?",
    "r9": "Send us an email at support@docmaster.com or use the \"Report a bug\" option in your profile. We will respond as soon as possible."
  },
